headline: 3 Reasons to Buy This Top Auto Stock Before It's Too Late
summary: General Motors has reduced its shares outstanding dramatically.  GM is rapidly expanding its EV sales in the U.S. and lowering costs.  The automaker's restructured business in China brought positive results.
